{"tid":777264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個問題想問好耐","createTime":"2018-08-12T17:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T02:31:17.000Z","uid":148201,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e43715936637648c9670467ba84b74d6993b1c57","tid":777264,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T17:38:44.000Z","msg":"就係細細個落街市買燒味飯嗰陣，都會發覺個燒味佬徒手斬燒味，然後再徒手找錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上每次買既燒味都會沾滿燒味佬既手汗(希望佢去完廁所有洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，仲會hi到D散銀同紙幣，究竟咁係咪正常?但係食足咁多年又無事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燒味佬既手汗先係精華，大快活嗰類快餐店既燒味飯就係少左呢樣靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好唔衛生，食餐燒味都加料比我"},{"pid":"557e72fc1cd1e63df60adaf7da039a06cd1d2202","tid":777264,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"703f50e78f9f67f7a3b590971f1577cb5fbbd254","tid":777264,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"第一、投你老母。<br />\n<br />\n第二、廚房佬真係垃撚圾去廁所抖完碌鳩唔洗手，食煙成身煙味，污鳩糟到黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9522fde188d70cfba3ebc5bc8d48fbe700e02153","tid":777264,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"同快餐帶著手套但成日都唔換一樣道理"},{"pid":"3110e40298492093a8ad9314f73fb9ea2e681505","tid":777264,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9522fde188d70cfba3ebc5bc8d48fbe700e02153","tid":777264,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"同快餐帶著手套但成日都唔換一樣道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"但係快餐起碼隔住手套，掂唔到散紙同手汗喎"}]}